  "recipeInstructions": "1. Prepare the bread using a light to medium crust setting on a white, sweet cycle. Do not use a timer.\n2. For the stuffing: Sauté the celery and onion in butter until soft. Toss with bread in a bowl. Add warmed broth and seasonings, then mix well until combined.\n3. Stuff the bird or bake the mixture in a covered casserole at 350°F for 20 minutes.",
